## Forms / selects

- **Select dropdown shows white text on white (unreadable options)**  
  Native `<select>` can inherit parent color; dropdown list may render with wrong contrast.  
  → Use `select select-theme` (and keep `input` or other layout classes) on every `<select>` so theme rules force readable background and text in light and dark mode.

- **ID number fields: consistent mask + optional scan**  
  Use `IdNumberInput` for any ID number input so we get hide/show (mask) and optional "Scan ID to capture number" in one place. Avoids duplication and keeps UX consistent (public triage guest/identity, staff triage Accept/New reg modals, TriageClientBinder).

