## Performance (desktop viewport)

- **Desktop-only lag: typing/click feels delayed, INP high, "Long interaction" in DevTools**  
  Full-viewport or large-area `backdrop-blur` is expensive on big viewports; presentation delay can reach hundreds of ms.  
  → Use `md:backdrop-blur-none` (and slightly more opaque bg, e.g. `md:bg-primary-600/95`) on headers, sidebars, and full-screen washes so desktop stays snappy; keep blur on mobile only.

